column2: SELECT    m.Objid, m.RA AS ra1, m.DEC AS dec1,    n.objid, o.ra, o.dec, o.petroMag_u, o.petroMagErr_u, o.petroMag_g, o.petroMagErr_g, o.petroMag_r,    o.petroMagErr_r, o.petroMag_i, o.petroMagErr_i, o.petroMag_z, o.petroMagErr_z, o.nChild, o.clean,    o.petroFlux_u, o.petroFlux_g, o.petroFlux_r, o.petroFlux_i, o.petroFlux_z, o.petroFluxIvar_u, o.petroFluxIvar_g,   o.petroFluxIvar_r, o.petroFluxIvar_i, o.petroFluxIvar_z,    o.ra AS ra2, o.dec AS dec2 into mydb.lowmassmag from MyDB.lowmass AS m     CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n     JOIN PhotoObjAll AS o ON n.objid=o.objid
